    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts precisely, making for a very comfortable and reliable driving experience. While the interior and exterior show some minor signs of normal use, there are no major mechanical issues or significant cosmetic defects to report. Potential buyers can expect a car that is ready for the road with plenty of life left, offering a great balance of performance and value.",
